note over browser:
https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/spa
page is loaded and the 'save' form button is pressed
end note

browser->browser: DOM is updated with the new item
browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa
note over server:
the server saves the data
from the POST request body
end note
server-->browser: application/json {"message":"note created"}
note over browser: 
console log: {"message":"note created"}
end note